{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/extras/discord-banner-600.gif?t=1735677709\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">RoboCo is a sandbox game about designing and building robots to serve the needs of squishy, hapless humans in the world of tomorrow! Create any robot you can imagine in the creative sandbox mode or take on unique challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/extras/RoboCo-Build-Any-Robot-You-Can-Imagine.png?t=1735677709\" />Snap together an expansive variety of parts to bring the machines of your dreams to life. Hook up controls, customize how your robots move and operate, then add fun cosmetics like googly eyes and hats!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/extras/Build-600.gif?t=1735677709\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/extras/RoboCo-Conquer-Challenges.png?t=1735677709\" />Put your engineering skills to the test in our tricky, open-ended challenges. Build custom robots to complete tasks like delivering sandwiches to hungry diners, preparing a romantic dinner, and showing off your robot dance moves!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/extras/Complete-600.gif?t=1735677709\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/extras/Steam-Program-Automated-Behaviors.png?t=1735677709\" />Tired of controllers? You have the option to use the powerful and easy-to-learn Python language to automate your creations and let your robots conquer the challenges while you kick back and relax!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/extras/automate-6002.gif?t=1735677709\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/extras/Steam-Share-Your-Innovations.png?t=1735677709\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Using Steam\u2019s built-in community workshop features, you can share your masterpieces with other robotics geniuses, or download others\u2019 robots for inspiration and remixing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/extras/Workshop-600.gif?t=1735677709\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735677709","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/page.bg.jpg?t=1735677709","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/5d907771705380e09f10b461928230462b153de4/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735677709","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/5d907771705380e09f10b461928230462b153de4/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735677709","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":30},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/extras/discord-banner-600.gif?t=1735677709\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">RoboCo is a sandbox game about designing and building robots to serve the needs of squishy, hapless humans in the world of tomorrow! Create any robot you can imagine in the creative sandbox mode or take on unique challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/extras/RoboCo-Build-Any-Robot-You-Can-Imagine.png?t=1735677709\" />Snap together an expansive variety of parts to bring the machines of your dreams to life. Hook up controls, customize how your robots move and operate, then add fun cosmetics like googly eyes and hats!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/extras/Build-600.gif?t=1735677709\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/extras/RoboCo-Conquer-Challenges.png?t=1735677709\" />Put your engineering skills to the test in our tricky, open-ended challenges. Build custom robots to complete tasks like delivering sandwiches to hungry diners, preparing a romantic dinner, and showing off your robot dance moves!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/extras/Complete-600.gif?t=1735677709\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067220/extras/Steam-Program-Automated-Behaviors.png?t=1735677709\" />Tired of controllers? You have the option to use the powerful and easy-to-learn Python language to automate your creations and let your robots conquer the challenges while you kick back and relax!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://share